</div>

<ul class="about-content">

<li>
Baddi University of Emerging Sciences and Technology, Makhnumajra,
Baddi, Dist. Solan (H.P.) has been operating under the aegis of the
Centre for Advanced Studies in Engineering since 2009.
</li>

<li>
The primary aims and objects of the society are to provide, offer,
promote and disseminate education at all levels of primary, middle,
higher secondary and higher education.
</li>

<li>
The society offers high quality and standardized education at
affordable rates with scholarships for economically weaker,
handicapped and meritorious students.
</li>

<li>
The university has a residential campus spread over 40 acres in
the picturesque slopes of Shivalik Hills at Baddi in Himachal Pradesh.
</li>

<li>
The institutes have built impressive infrastructure for academics,
co-curricular and sports activities.
</li>

<li>
Separate hostels for boys and girls, modern classrooms,
well-equipped laboratories and rich libraries support students'
learning environment.
</li>

</ul>

